arts.ttl: Armenia captain 'lost his head' - Republic of Ireland's Azaz on red card
arts.sum: Republic of Ireland's Finn Azaz says Armenian captain Tigran Barseghyan "lost his head" when he was sent off for headbutting the Irish midfielder.

arts.ttl: Ferguson header to beat Armenia keeps Ireland's World Cup hopes alive
arts.sum: Evan Ferguson's fourth goal in five competitive internationals kept the Republic of Ireland's World Cup dream alive as they edged past 10-man Armenia to claim their first Group F victory.

arts.ttl: Heimir Hallgrimsson: Win all that matters as Republic of Ireland face Armenia
arts.sum: Ireland have taken just one point from their first three qualifiers.
